![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8208967d-a3b7-4a2e-b976-34071ceb49c2/Screenshot+2025-12-11+162427.png?format=original)

The Major Issues Podcast celebrates the 20th anniversary of _Infinite Crisis_ with a massive, all-in deep dive into the entire explosive road that led to DC’s universe-shattering event. From _Identity Crisis_ and _Countdown to Infinite Crisis_ to _The OMAC Project_, _Day of Vengeance_, _Villains United_, and the _Rann–Thanagar War_, the hosts break down every twist, betrayal, uprising, and cosmic wildfire that dragged the DC Universe to its absolute breaking point. It’s the ultimate, high-energy guided tour through the chaos, the shocks, and the long-burning fuse that made _Infinite Crisis_ not just inevitable—but unforgettable.

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

